  - Controls: First, Step back, Play/Pause, Step forward, Last (left to right).
  - Frame change: map updates; current point highlighted; popup (vehicle, event, sensor, speed).
  - Click map point: navigate to time snapshot details.
  - UI: back button has more right margin.
  - API integration per TA5/TF2.

